- update to 2.9v:
- cfdisk no longer believes the kernel's HDGETGEO
	(and may be able to partition a 2 TB disk)

* 五 7月 16 1999 Jeff Johnson <jbj@redhat.com>
- update to 2.9u:
- Czech more.help and messages (Jiri Pavlovsky)
